high_descs: turn right and move towards the window, then turn left around the middle table and face it
pick up the medium sized pan on the table in front of the milk bottle
turn around and face the sink
place the pan in the kitchen sink, then turn the sink on and fill the pan with water. Pick it up out of the sink
turn around and face the table again
place the water filled pan on the far left corner of the table
anns.task_desc: Fill a pan with water from the kitchen sink

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the far side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the dirty bowl that is closest to the bottle of wine on the kitchen island.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the dirty bowl in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bowl filled with water.
Turn around and take a step forward so you are facing the kitchen island.
Put the clean bowl of water on the island on the left corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bowl of water on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn to your right move forward the turn left then head towards the the table facing the two chairs
Pick up the bowl in front of you beside the clear bottle
Turn to your left and head to the sink
Put the bowl in the sink then rinse it and fill it with water
Pick up the bowl with water then turn around to your right facing the table
Put the bowl on the left side edge of the table
anns.task_desc: Put bowl with water on the table
